org.artorg.tools.phantomData.server.boot

Class PropertiesBooter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.artorg.tools.phantomData.server.boot.Booter
      • org.artorg.tools.phantomData.server.boot.PropertiesBooter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServerBooter

    public abstract class PropertiesBooter
extends Booter
    Booter with two external configuration files. Call init() for booting. The path of the two config files cannot changed by a setting. The files will be searched in parentDirectory/phantomData/config. The parent directory is the directory where the runnable *.jar file is placed.

    application.properties

    Contains settings for Spring and the database.

    config.properties

    Contains general settings whose are defined in this project. The are not given by frameworks.
    See Also:
    PropertiesFile
